以上 100 千米，也就是著名的冯卡门线。这个数字并不是拍脑袋想出来的。冯卡门作为钱学森先生的导师，在空气动力学和轨道动力学方面都有着开创性的成就。我们知道，飞机在空气空间里飞行，要依靠机身和机翼与空气的相对运动来产生升力，高度越大、空气越稀薄，飞机就要飞得更快，才能产生足够升力。但是到了 100 千米的高度，飞行速度要超过每秒 7800 米的第一宇宙速度，才能产生超过自重的升力。然而飞到这个速度，飞行器就进入了轨道飞行，空气动力学原则不再适用，要改用轨道动力学来分析弹道了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-ca9651fbb61af6440622854ad31c0bad_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "261 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445946498"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ilreo0/DU7PwdEAMaCDYxMzc3ODM5IOf20oEGMA04uwRAFHIJNDQ1OTQ2NDk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1614175852.0615108", "card_id": "Q_20057134", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在眼镜发明之前，近视了的人是怎样生活的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在眼镜发明之前也是有近视眼出现的吧？ 他们是怎样生活的呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "258 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/20057134"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIlreo0/DU7PwdEAMaBjIwMjg5MiD23875BDACONADQBVyCDIwMDU3MTM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1614175852.0617723", "card_id": "Q_445746953", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 52}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "贵州茅台股价跌破 2300 元，白酒股是否已站上山顶？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2 月 22 日，白酒股大跌，截至收盘，贵州茅台下跌 6.99%，报收 2288.02 元，跌破 2300 元。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-02157ca32c2a3a5c5c157b10e067e8a4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "249 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445746953"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ilreo0/DU7PwdEAMaCDYxMzMzNTIwIOmyzYEGMAU4ugFAFnIJNDQ1NzQ2OTUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_